                  </persName>
            . I produce the handkerchief, which I received from the witness - I saw nothing of the transaction.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18340703-57-person449">
                  WILLIAM 
                  MACLENNAN
               <interp inst="t18340703-57-person449" type="surname" value="MACLENNAN"></interp>
